        <div class="commentContent">Please ensure your city does accept bottle caps and lids before putting them in recycling.  The city of Seattle and King County, Washington only accept lids MORE THAN THREE INCHES in diameter.  Smaller lids jam the machines used by city of Seattle for recycling.

Washington State residents, support lawmakers who support more advanced recycling options!

Cities with more advanced recycling programs, please share your stories with law makers and get them to adopt the idea in other cities.

Thank you Whole Foods for accepting recycling not currently available through government options.

