        <div class="commentContent">I am an early childhood teacher.  I save my caps to use with my students.  We use them for sorting activities.  They can sort them by size, color and other characteristics.  They can describe how they are the same or different.  I encourage parents to let their children make bottle cap collections to sort at home.</div>
